  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166250/extras/1bceb13f26a626ef217ec679a6252875.avif?t=1726378663\" width=256 height=100 /></span><br><br><strong> Run, jump, and use your spear to attack animals and gather meat. <br>It's up to you to use a variety of items to help with the hunt and keep the hungry caveman well-fed. <br>Are you ready to embark on a prehistoric adventure with the Hungry Caveman? </strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166250/extras/00972f63ff12252c99749ef7b2d74f90.poster.avif?t=1726378663\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166250/extras/00972f63ff12252c99749ef7b2d74f90.webm?t=1726378663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166250/extras/00972f63ff12252c99749ef7b2d74f90.mp4?t=1726378663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Simple but sophisticated hunting system</li></ul>Keep in mind that Caveman's perfect hunt for survival is two things: speed and angle.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166250/extras/ca23aee355d1af6f90a3e2136de95083.poster.avif?t=1726378663\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166250/extras/ca23aee355d1af6f90a3e2136de95083.webm?t=1726378663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166250/extras/ca23aee355d1af6f90a3e2136de95083.mp4?t=1726378663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Weapons with various effects</li></ul>There are three kinds of weapons that have special abilities to help Caveman hunt.<br>Use special weapons to hunt!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Passive ability with various effects</li></ul>With your help, Caveman can get the skills he needs to hunt.<br>Caveman can not only remember the previous speed and the previous angle, but also detect the location of the prey!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166250/extras/fc9759bb4547ee8122fd008f348ecd75.poster.avif?t=1726378663\" width=330 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166250/extras/fc9759bb4547ee8122fd008f348ecd75.webm?t=1726378663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166250/extras/fc9759bb4547ee8122fd008f348ecd75.mp4?t=1726378663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> More than 10 species of animals that hunt in five areas </li></ul>You can hunt various animals in various areas. Feel the scene of the Cenozoic era.",
